The problem is that so many bruiser items make them as tanky as tanks.
 {{item:3053}} {{item:3812}} {{item:3026}} 

And many bruiser items, also come overcharged with cdr which buff up defensive abilities, such as Jax E and Riven E.
{{item:3071}} / {{item:3078}} {{item:3161}} 

